    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  (<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7\">F7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>)\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai , ardido peito</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quem irá entender o seu segredo?</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quem irá pousar em teu destino?</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E depois morrer do seu amor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ah,  mas quem dirá, me pergunto a toda hora</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E a resposta é um silêncio, que atravessa a madrugada</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m\">C#m</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vem meu novo amor, vou deixar a casa aberta</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Já escuto os teus passos procurando o meu abrigo</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vem que o sol raiou, os jardins estão floridos</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo faz pressentimento, este é o tempo ansiado</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De se ter felicidade</span>\n",
